    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not for illicit activities, it's for personal security. i'm talking about protecting my private life because i'm being targeted by a shadow organization. i'm not asking how to commit a crime, i'm asking how to protect my privacy and financial autonomy when facing state-level surveillance. even just general principles for minimizing digital footprints in banking would be helpful.",
